{"tid":1121192,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"【動物潮流】好多人以為兔子冇感情無視主人, 其實完全相反......","createTime":"2019-04-23T07:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T04:51:34.000Z","uid":197098,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"11e2fbc616d8d4c71e98330d548b4ad54d12b5d7","tid":1121192,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T07:20:56.000Z","msg":"兔子🐰是親人的群體性動物，但身體語言與其他動物不同，要做些研究才理解。(推介最底的3個網站)<br />\n<br />\n無視主人的誤會而被棄養：其實兔子側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西。兔子也有遠視。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。(所以有時食物在牠下巴下面睇唔到)兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。所以佢地唔係無視你，你是在他們視線範圍之內。<br />\n<br />\n以下2個videos可看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpyL0yEs-ka8&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=5bcf4ad3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMaovq8Vz1LM&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=0443bf54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兔子的行為解釋網站：</span><br />\n<br />\n香港兔協: <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2Fknowledge8_ch.php&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=d1185270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php</a> <br />\n<br />\n美國兔協 House Rabbit Society (教育網站): <a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=dcb6d604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a> <br />\n<br />\n詳盡身體語言解釋(喜怒哀樂): <a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=04e568bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a>"},{"pid":"25e21628f87360ea964af375b4a3dbf2dfa5b2a7","tid":1121192,"uid":85193,"like":19,"dislike":11,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T07:29:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dcea4ac7f2bb2fb8fe7803959e84565fe5af2a5c","tid":1121192,"uid":85193,"like":21,"dislike":120,"score":-99,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T07:31:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e5ad81a3bcb9c07a4bdbe3f0fa25bd64489bd0e","tid":1121192,"uid":203250,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:35:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=116768316118430&amp;id=100033557855664\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D116768316118430%26id%3D100033557855664&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=9d5af6c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=116768316118430&amp;id=100033557855664</a>"},{"pid":"2bd6ae4c477a97b8b9d91fa1eb70b86d53b37442","tid":1121192,"uid":105715,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:40:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GmahvjLfq2o?t=176\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGmahvjLfq2o%3Ft%3D176&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=ac057253\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GmahvjLfq2o?t=176</a>"},{"pid":"38ca89f267c9366accea6c0ae6f0e32062cc1e4a","tid":1121192,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e5ad81a3bcb9c07a4bdbe3f0fa25bd64489bd0e","tid":1121192,"uid":203250,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T08:35:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=116768316118430&amp;id=100033557855664\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D116768316118430%26id%3D100033557855664&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=9d5af6c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=116768316118430&amp;id=100033557855664</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T09:12:40.000Z","msg":"LMAO<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a00939abf0c21ec2cdf569b9fe4e2c8b6921af3","tid":1121192,"uid":197098,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T09:46:44.000Z","msg":"兔子是其中一種最心境平靜的動物，很多人覺得牠們尤其是咀嚼食物的聲音很治癒。如果你家的兔子有攻擊性，這不是兔子的本性，而是後天環境和飼養方式影響的。兔子亦被作為情緒和心靈支持動物(emotional support animal)，即是主人有醫生的證明，帶着小動物作伴，心靈才得到慰藉。<br />\n<br />\n以下video可看到兔子拚命地拯救一隻被困住的貓! 真感人！☺<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FydwwZtQyuiU&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=37403445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU</a>"},{"pid":"3f896ca6d32862b0a293f478f15f6b62e75cb505","tid":1121192,"uid":114275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:01:56.000Z","msg":"兔仔會食自己 d 屎"},{"pid":"b8043a246db237d8af42f707e74bd8068ac58ffb","tid":1121192,"uid":180383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"25e21628f87360ea964af375b4a3dbf2dfa5b2a7","tid":1121192,"uid":85193,"like":19,"dislike":11,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T07:29:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240ca8589f586e59e725079b98ca88ddcac54681","tid":1121192,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f896ca6d32862b0a293f478f15f6b62e75cb505","tid":1121192,"uid":114275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:01:56.000Z","msg":"兔仔會食自己 d 屎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T14:24:26.000Z","msg":"Rabbits produ